vyges-vt-swap performs STA-driven threshold-voltage swapping (iso-footprint) to cut
leakage while holding timing, or to close setup — netlist in, resized netlist out.

Per-foundry calibration data and plugins, where applicable, are distributed
separately under their own terms and are not part of this repository.
